Author: webtrauma
Text: Electrolytes and water. If you feel like shit please eat something

Author: ynotlovee
Text: Always keep water in arms reach, also low calorie healthy foods like cucumber or other raw veggies in case you feel weak and need to break fast, its important that the first thing you put into your body after a period of fasting is something nutritious and not heavy on your digestion :) Good luck, stay safe
